{"tid":388314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"郵局職員西環墮海溺斃","createTime":"2017-09-05T11:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T11:29:46.000Z","uid":29609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ed7cbfa0498ab8405d20e20b8042828eb8374205","tid":388314,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T11:25:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170905/57173047\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170905%2F57173047&d=z0qExKJve019zTluS%2Ft0s%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=53fb55ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170905%2F57173047&h=fcf0114f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170905/57173047</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170905/large/1504609037_ffdd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170905%2Flarge%2F1504609037_ffdd.jpg&h=6a2e1458&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西環發生懷疑墮海溺斃事件，下午4時許，有市民報案，指於西環城西道巴士站附近碼頭上岸期間，於離岸1米的海面發現有人載浮載沉。消防及警員接報趕至，將一名男子救起，他已陷入昏迷，由救護車送住瑪麗醫院搶救，惜終告不治。<br />\n<br />\n死者姓梁(37歲)，被發現時身上孭著一個背囊，警方未有撿獲遺書，正聯絡其家人了解，並調查其墮海原因。據悉，梁家住沙田，於郵政局任職，今日放假。<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"22fe344633bdf2ae883ca296cc9f6c8b7a98e6c9","tid":388314,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T11:26:54.000Z","msg":"7月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb28127f71e43b016652073ca2d0d96023851cd5","tid":388314,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T11:27:39.000Z","msg":"鬼門關大開"},{"pid":"65e010966bdfd341d506caaca845cf16cdd6bdaa","tid":388314